l-GDPR: Hija meħtieġa azzjoni"],"Some points carry an elevated risk and should be resolved promptly.":["Xi punti jġorru riskju elevat u għandhom jiġu solvuti malajr."],"Copied to clipboard":["Ikkupjat fil-clipboard"],"Paste the snippet into your privacy policy.":["Waħħal il-biċċa fil-politika tal-privatezza tiegħek."],"Copy failed":["L-ikkupjar falla"],"Please select and copy the text manually.":["Jekk jogħġbok agħżel u kkopja t-test manwalment."],"For your configuration":["Għall-konfigurazzjoni tiegħek"],"Loading privacy status …":["Qed jiġi mgħobbi l-istatus tal-privatezza …"],"Privacy":["Privatezza"],"Status, recommendations and ready-to-use snippets for your privacy policy.":["Status, rakkomandazzjonijiet u biċċiet lesti għall-użu għall-politika tal-privatezza tiegħek."],"Fill in the [ … ] placeholders before publishing.":["Imla l-placeholders [ … ] qabel il-pubblikazzjoni."],"Determined automatically from your current configuration.":["Iddeterminat awtomatikament mill-konfigurazzjoni attwali tiegħek."],"Open":["Iftaħ"],"Confirmations":["Konfermi"],"Points the plugin cannot detect automatically. Confirm them once done.":["Punti li l-plugin ma jistax jindividwa awtomatikament. Ikkonfermahom ladarba jsiru."],"The privacy snippet is included in my privacy policy.":["Il-biċċa tal-privatezza hija inkluża fil-politika tal-privatezza tiegħi."],"A data processing agreement (DPA, Art. 28 GDPR) with the API provider is in place.":["Ftehim ta' pproċessar tad-data (DPA, Art. 28 GDPR) mal-fornitur tal-API jeżisti."],"Note: Confirmations apply to the entire website and are recorded in the audit log with timestamp and user.":["Nota: Il-konfermi japplikaw għall-websajt kollha u jiġu rreġistrati fir-reġistru tal-awditjar bit-timestamp u l-utent."],"Snippets":["Biċċiet"],"Snippet A — Local mode (without API)":["Biċċa A — Modalità lokali (mingħajr API)"],"Snippet B — With SilentShield API":["Biċċa B — Bl-API SilentShield"],"IP storage pseudonymized":["Ħażna tal-IP psewdonimizzata"],"IP addresses are stored only in salted-hashed form, never in plain text.":["L-indirizzi IP jinħażnu biss f'forma salted-hashed, qatt f'test ċar."],"Plain-text logging active":["Reġistrazzjoni f'test ċar attiva"],"Form data is stored unmasked and may contain personal data. Disable it or strictly limit retention.":["Id-data tal-formola tinħażen mhux moħbija u tista' tinkludi data personali. Iddiżattivaha jew illimita ż-żamma b'mod strett."],"Open logging setting":["Iftaħ is-setting tar-reġistrazzjoni"],"Logs are masked":["Ir-reġistri huma moħbija"],"Sensitive form fields (email, password, IP) are masked before storage.":["Il-kampijiet sensittivi tal-formola (email, password, IP) jiġu moħbija qabel il-ħażna."],"Retention period not limited":["Il-perjodu ta' żamma mhux limitat"],"At least one active log has no automatic deletion deadline. Configure a retention limit.":["Mill-inqas reġistru attiv wieħed ma għandux skadenza ta' tħassir awtomatiku. Ikkonfigura limitu ta' żamma."],"Configure retention period":["Ikkonfigura l-perjodu ta' żamma"],"Retention period configured":["Il-perjodu ta' żamma kkonfigurat"],"Logs are deleted automatically once the configured period expires.":["Ir-reġistri jitħassru awtomatikament ladarba jiskadi l-perjodu kkonfigurat."],"Privacy notice included":["Avviż dwar il-privatezza inkluż"],"You confirmed that the appropriate privacy snippet is included in your privacy policy.":["Ikkonfermajt li l-biċċa tal-privatezza xierqa hija inkluża fil-politika tal-privatezza tiegħek."],"Privacy notice recommended":["Avviż dwar il-privatezza rrakkomandat"],"Because data is transmitted to the SilentShield API, this must be stated in your privacy policy. Use the snippet below and confirm.":["Peress li d-data tintbagħat lill-API SilentShield, dan irid jiġi ddikjarat fil-politika tal-privatezza tiegħek. Uża l-biċċa hawn taħt u kkonferma."],"The processing of IP addresses should be stated in your privacy policy. Use the snippet below and confirm.":["L-ipproċessar tal-indirizzi IP għandu jiġi ddikjarat fil-politika tal-privatezza tiegħek. Uża l-biċċa hawn taħt u kkonferma."],"Show snippet":["Uri l-biċċa"],"Processing in Germany":["Ipproċessar fil-Ġermanja"],"The SilentShield API processes data exclusively on servers in Germany (Hetzner) — no third-country transfer.":["L-API SilentShield tipproċessa d-data esklussivament fuq servers fil-Ġermanja (Hetzner) — l-ebda trasferiment lejn pajjiż terz."],"Data processing agreement in place":["Ftehim ta' pproċessar tad-data fis-seħħ"],"You confirmed that a DPA (Art. 28 GDPR) has been concluded with the API provider.":["Ikkonfermajt li ġie konkluż ftehim ta' pproċessar tad-data (Art. 28 GDPR) mal-fornitur tal-API."],"Data processing agreement required":["Ftehim ta' pproċessar tad-data meħtieġ"],"When the API is active, a data processing agreement (Art. 28 GDPR) with the provider is mandatory. Conclude it and confirm.":["Meta l-API tkun attiva, ftehim ta' pproċessar tad-data (Art. 28 GDPR) mal-fornitur huwa obbligatorju. Ikkonkludih u kkonferma."],"Learn more":["Itgħallem aktar"],"Open privacy details":["Iftaħ id-dettalji tal-privatezza"],"Legal note: The text snippets, checks and recommendations provided are intended solely for general guidance and do not constitute legal advice. They do not replace an individual review by a lawyer or a data protection officer. No liability is assumed for their accuracy, completeness or timeliness. Ensuring legally compliant implementation on your website is your sole responsibility.":["Nota legali: Is-siltiet ta' test, il-verifiki u r-rakkomandazzjonijiet ipprovduti huma maħsuba biss għal gwida ġenerali u ma jikkostitwixxux parir legali. Dawn ma jissostitwixxux reviżjoni individwali minn avukat jew minn uffiċjal tal-protezzjoni tad-data. Ma tiġi assunta l-ebda responsabbiltà għall-eżattezza, il-kompletezza jew l-attwalità tagħhom. Li tiżgura implimentazzjoni konformi mal-liġi fuq is-sit web tiegħek hija r-responsabbiltà tiegħek biss."],"Not legal advice – no warranty. Please have it reviewed by a lawyer.":["Mhux parir legali – mingħajr garanzija. Jekk jogħġbok ġiegħlu jiġi rivedut minn avukat."],"Spam protection (SilentShield \/ Captcha for Contact Form 7)\n\nTo protect our forms against automated submissions (spam), we use the “SilentShield” plugin. When a form is submitted, the following data is processed:\n\n- your IP address – exclusively in shortened and hashed form, in order to detect repeated or mass submissions;\n- technical verification features such as timestamps of when the form is loaded and submitted, browser and JavaScript signals, and a hidden verification field (honeypot).\n\nThis data is processed exclusively on our own server or in our website database and is not transmitted to third parties. It serves solely to detect and prevent abusive, automated access.\n\nThe legal basis is our legitimate interest in preventing spam and abuse (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR). The data is automatically deleted after [30 \/ 60 \/ 90] days.":["Protezzjoni kontra l-ispam (SilentShield \/ Captcha for Contact Form 7)\n\nBiex nipproteġu l-formoli tagħna kontra sottomissjonijiet awtomatizzati (spam), nużaw il-plugin “SilentShield”. Meta tiġi sottomessa formola, jiġu pproċessati d-data li ġejja:\n\n- l-indirizz IP tiegħek – esklussivament f'forma mqassra u hashed, sabiex jiġu identifikati sottomissjonijiet ripetuti jew bil-massa;\n- karatteristiċi tekniċi ta' verifika bħal timestamps ta' meta l-formola tiġi mgħobbija u sottomessa, sinjali tal-browser u tal-JavaScript, u kamp ta' verifika moħbi (honeypot).\n\nDin id-data tiġi pproċessata esklussivament fuq is-server tagħna stess jew fil-bażi tad-data tas-sit web tagħna u ma tiġix trażmessa lil partijiet terzi. Hija sservi biss biex jiġi identifikat u evitat aċċess abbużiv u awtomatizzat.\n\nIl-bażi legali hija l-interess leġittimu tagħna fil-prevenzjoni tal-ispam u tal-abbuż (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR). Id-data titħassar awtomatikament wara [30 \/ 60 \/ 90] ġurnata."],"Spam protection with the SilentShield API\n\nTo protect our forms against spam and bots, we use the “SilentShield” service. When a form is loaded and submitted, technical characteristics of your access are processed and transmitted to the SilentShield API for assessment:\n\n- your IP address;\n- behavioural and device information (e.g. timestamps, interaction and input signals, browser properties);\n- the URL of the page accessed.\n\nBased on this data, SilentShield determines whether the input is likely human or automated and returns an assessment result.\n\nThe provider and recipient of the data is Forge12 Interactive GmbH, Josefstr. 37, 78166 Donaueschingen, which carries out the processing as a processor on our behalf (data processing agreement pursuant to Art. 28 GDPR). Processing takes place exclusively on servers in Germany (Hetzner Online GmbH); no transfer to third countries takes place.\n\nThe legal basis is our legitimate interest in preventing spam and abuse (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR). The transmitted technical access data is stored by SilentShield only for as long as is necessary for spam detection (generally a maximum of 14 days, unless security-relevant events require longer storage) and is then deleted.\n\nFurther information: https:\/\/silentshield.io\/en\/privacy":["Protezzjoni kontra l-ispam bl-API ta' SilentShield\n\nBiex nipproteġu l-formoli tagħna kontra l-ispam u l-bots, nużaw is-servizz “SilentShield”. Meta formola tiġi mgħobbija u sottomessa, karatteristiċi tekniċi tal-aċċess tiegħek jiġu pproċessati u trażmessi lill-API ta' SilentShield għall-evalwazzjoni:\n\n- l-indirizz IP tiegħek;\n- informazzjoni dwar l-imġiba u dwar l-apparat (eż. timestamps, sinjali ta' interazzjoni u ta' input, proprjetajiet tal-browser);\n- l-URL tal-paġna li ġiet aċċessata.\n\nFuq il-bażi ta' din id-data, SilentShield jiddetermina jekk l-input x'aktarx huwiex uman jew awtomatizzat u jirritorna riżultat ta' evalwazzjoni.\n\nIl-fornitur u r-riċevitur tad-data huwa Forge12 Interactive GmbH, Josefstr. 37, 78166 Donaueschingen, li jwettaq l-ipproċessar bħala proċessur f'isimna (ftehim dwar l-ipproċessar tad-data skont l-Art. 28 GDPR). L-ipproċessar iseħħ esklussivament fuq servers fil-Ġermanja (Hetzner Online GmbH); ma sseħħ l-ebda trasferiment lejn pajjiżi terzi.\n\nIl-bażi legali hija l-interess leġittimu tagħna fil-prevenzjoni tal-ispam u tal-abbuż (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR). Id-data teknika tal-aċċess trażmessa tinżamm minn SilentShield biss għaż-żmien meħtieġ għall-identifikazzjoni tal-ispam (ġeneralment massimu ta' 14-il ġurnata, sakemm avvenimenti relatati mas-sigurtà ma jirrikjedux ħżin itwal) u mbagħad titħassar.\n\nAktar informazzjoni: https:\/\/silentshield.io\/en\/privacy"]}}}